{"tid":965267,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"facebook留言罵人「有頭無腦」 台灣2網友被判侮辱罪成立，罰款3千元","createTime":"2019-01-02T02:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T14:07:40.000Z","uid":100680,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"796182470a21435e33cdbda893230e3730992ea4","tid":965267,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T02:06:37.000Z","msg":"新北市2名男網友前年在李婉鈺臉書專頁留言，罵她「有頭無腦的人」、「假鬼假怪」等字句，李婉鈺得知後氣憤提告，新北地院依公然侮辱罪判兩人罰金3千元。而選議員失利的李婉鈺許久沒現身，聖誕節當天自拍影片祝網友聖誕快樂，看得出心情已經恢復了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2018/12/27/1545926003_70045.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2018%2F12%2F27%2F1545926003_70045.jpg&h=06d84214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n時任新北市議員李婉鈺：「Merry Christmas，好久不見。」<br />\n角逐議員落馬的李婉鈺，許久沒現身她，在聖誕節當天，穿著一身桃紅針織衫自拍影片，祝網友聖誕快樂，李婉鈺看起來神清氣爽，坦言自己這陣子都在沉澱，思考下一步。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2018/12/27/1545926036_95802.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2018%2F12%2F27%2F1545926036_95802.jpg&h=4f9e21bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李婉鈺在臉書上PO出一張和劉建國的親密照，隔幾天又PO出分手流淚照，沒想到卻引來網友酸言酸語，一名周姓網友就留言，「有頭無腦的人呀，把頭當做裝飾品在使用，愧對父母和自己」，還有一名王姓網友跟著罵「想想你李婉鈺三個字代表什麼，維基百科都查得到，笑死人了，假鬼假怪」等留言，讓李婉鈺氣得提告。<br />\n<br />\n▼（圖／東森新聞）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2018/12/27/1545926043_85902.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2018%2F12%2F27%2F1545926043_85902.jpg&h=245b679b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩名網友到案後都表示，自己留言沒有針對任何人，只是單純就做人做事來評論，但新北地院不採信，認為兩人留言是針對李婉鈺PO文獨立回應，足以構成貶損個人人格，會引起他人不快，屬於侮辱性言詞，依法判罰兩人3000元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ebc.net.tw/News/Article/145688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ebc.net.tw%2FNews%2FArticle%2F145688&d=0H%2Friwu7FwwZDgfqMGtu88mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=3654ca9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ebc.net.tw/News/Article/145688</a>"},{"pid":"b7aa5d21fa1a81850865e8ff27869c451776386a","tid":965267,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T02:08:19.000Z","msg":"台灣中国化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48029851e156ad54ee37644a88dc3b10e4174809","tid":965267,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T02:09:30.000Z","msg":"on9 台仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee96183ecd0e7aa28216f90ea9be914593fc36b","tid":965267,"uid":28720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T02:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46d040db8b155675e4cee907b4ce09130906f42","tid":965267,"uid":100680,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"b7aa5d21fa1a81850865e8ff27869c451776386a","tid":965267,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T02:08:19.000Z","msg":"台灣中国化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T02:15:33.000Z","msg":"除左有投票權，台灣本身就同中國無分別<br />\n繁體支那"},{"pid":"a6ed3419def8b0967b32435b9dbc407e6e9e7206","tid":965267,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c59be3b69850f8cb6e3feced7602189756b15c","tid":965267,"uid":17103,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:31:08.000Z","msg":"台灣真係好小朋友 ... 你屌柒人會罰錢 ... <br />\n真係唔撚明一個島國可以變到點"},{"pid":"8abb7f2af9f3c734407c56780df46d359e478c01","tid":965267,"uid":51565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:38:44.000Z","msg":"新北市又得分"},{"pid":"9d3c24f55b4c64cf523528f5277f1acd7938fcbf","tid":965267,"uid":18241,"l